<template>
  <svg
    width="24"
    height="24"
    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
    fill="none"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
  >
    <g id="alert/error_outline_24px">
      <path
        id="icon/outlined/alert/error_outline_24px"
        fill-rule="evenodd"
        clip-rule="evenodd"
        d="M11.99 2C6.47 2 2 6.48 2 12C2 17.52 6.47 22 11.99 22C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12C22 6.48 17.52 2 11.99 2ZM13 13V7H11V13H13ZM13 17V15H11V17H13ZM4 12C4 16.42 7.58 20 12 20C16.42 20 20 16.42 20 12C20 7.58 16.42 4 12 4C7.58 4 4 7.58 4 12Z"
        :fill="changeColor"
      />
    </g>
  </svg>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "SvgIconFault",
  props: {
    status: {
      type: Object,
      default: () => {
        return {};
      },
    },
  },
  computed: {
    changeColor() {
      if (this.status == 1) {
        return "#6FCF97";
      } else {
        if (this.status == 0) return "#B7B7B7";
        else return "#EB5757";
      }
    },
  },
};
</script>

<style></style>
